member.example:
This sample shows how to call HelloAsync.

JsonMergePatchClient client = new JsonMergePatchClient();

Response response = await client.HelloAsync();

Console.WriteLine(response.Status);

This sample shows how to call HelloAsync with all request content.

JsonMergePatchClient client = new JsonMergePatchClient();

Response response = await client.HelloAsync();

Console.WriteLine(response.Status);

